Because while vegetarians allow themselves to eat cream cakes, ice cream, or a hearty edamer, these are not on a vegan's menu.
Milk, cheese, eggs, meat and fish are all avoided, and the vegan also refuses all animal products.
What remains, you may wonder, but on closer inspection the vegan world is remarkably inventive.
